From chaco001 at umn.edu  Thu Feb 23 21:56:22 2017
From: chaco001 at umn.edu (Jeremy Chacon)
Date: Thu, 23 Feb 2017 14:56:22 -0600
Subject: [R-sig-eco] what's the best R implementation of a Logistic
